properties.areaDesc: San Francisco Bay South of the Bay Bridge; San Pablo Bay, Suisun Bay, the West Delta and  the San Francisco Bay north of the Bay Bridge
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 16 at 9:02AM PST until January 16 at 12:00PM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 20 to 30 kt with gusts up to 40 kt and
very rough waters.

* WHERE...San Pablo Bay, Suisun Bay, the West Delta and the San
Francisco Bay north of the Bay Bridge and San Francisco Bay
South of the Bay Bridge.

* WHEN...Until noon PST today.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL NOON PST TODAY... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY HAS EXPIRED
